{"tid":56245,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南港島巴士綫重組, $4.7變$10.9","createTime":"2016-12-27T05:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T10:47:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4d9e74237d12bfec0fd3cee645a85b7a74200f4","tid":56245,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=205223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D205223&d=ho%2FvgKfURKTm3ZkMQb2G0X8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=b9e3de4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D205223&h=8891e414\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=205223</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/130005_cb5b5f9b550b19d088736995abf76d3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F130005_cb5b5f9b550b19d088736995abf76d3d.png&h=dbdb8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/130006_964bff184499d5ae825270381c214537.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F130006_964bff184499d5ae825270381c214537.png&h=6c903009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】港鐵南港島綫明天開通，區內多條巴士小巴路線分階段重組。當中，包括多條原本行走南港島綫未能覆蓋的地區會被削減和取消，區內居民和關注組都批評重組方案令他們少了選擇。<br />\n<br />\n香港仔隧道每天早上都塞車，南區居民已經忍受多年，港鐵南港島綫開通後，終於有多一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n南港島綫往來金鐘至海怡半島，途徑海洋公園、黃竹坑和利東，但同樣位處於南區的華富、華貴、置富和香港仔等，居民未能直接受惠。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署會重組區內的公共交通服務，配合南港島綫開通，首階段會增設多條小巴線及調整現有巴士路線，接駁港鐵黃竹坑站。不過，價錢要貴一點。<br />\n<br />\n以南港島綫未有覆蓋的香港仔為例，現時可乘搭城巴70號或37A，經香港仔隧道直達中環、金鐘，車費4.7元。日後若想乘搭港鐵，便要駁多一程小巴，車費合共10.9元，足足貴一倍。<br />\n<br />\n到第二階段的重組計劃，12條巴士線因為與南港島綫重疊，有機會被取消。逾20條巴士線會削減班次，當中，有多條路線是原本行走南港島綫未能覆蓋的地區。<br />\n<br />\n有關注團體批評重組計劃未有周詳考慮，削減和取消的巴士線太多，令居民搭車選擇減少。"},{"pid":"cb9c46d6050b06dcb99cb68daf460788a9f2d0dc","tid":56245,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"玩死哂平交通工具<br />\n迫人搭貴價地鐵"},{"pid":"a4854ef59ecafefb71786b0e0033dbd8a1aa013f","tid":56245,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"港鐵高層死全家"},{"pid":"4083a8cab702208ebba05ce236ef99e39e03ffc4","tid":56245,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"住香港仔應該撘小巴巴士方便好多。"},{"pid":"fc5628e82e161d0a4e84bdd6d6cadbcc97d62f11","tid":56245,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d099b287f101d7cd2cd837937192e62fbe79a5","tid":56245,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e08c5a73692dd1db54bbd97b241dc9185c4679","tid":56245,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4a3a95fc6044d08dfec690a5ffb6bf670315f7e","tid":56245,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83c80cffedb0fa8b5f0aac84031e59b3ecb516aa","tid":56245,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:21:23.000Z","msg":"70，72，37a 應該唔會cut"},{"pid":"acc236ce1d846d888dde7604b13a4cdee0534e55","tid":56245,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港鐵高層死全家</blockquote><br />\n馬時亨話市民死哂都未到佢"},{"pid":"920f01363d909a143931253a2f352cfb0718ffd8","tid":56245,"uid":35107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"係啲南區群組睇到南區班人J到出晒血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5beaba4c6cbb05c099d0251cd6f8dc76cb